<inglise> COUNCIL REGULATION (EEC) No 3509/80 of 22 December 1980 amending, consequent on Greek accession, Regulations (EEC) No 729/70 and (EEC) No 355/77 as regards the adaptation of certain amounts which may be charged to the EAGGF, Guidance Section </inglise>
<eesti> N&Otilde;UKOGU M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (EM&Uuml;) nr 3509/80, millega Kreeka &uuml;hinemise t&otilde;ttu muudetakse m&auml;&auml;rusi (EM&Uuml;) nr 729/70 ja (EM&Uuml;) nr 355/77 teatavate summade kohandamise osas, mida v&otilde;ib katta EAGGFi arendusrahastust 22. detsember 1980 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COUNCIL OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE N&Otilde;UKOGU, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Economic Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Majandus&uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the 1979 Act of Accession, and in particular Article 146 (2) thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse 1979. aasta &uuml;hinemisakti, eriti selle artikli 146 l&otilde;iget 2, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the proposal from the Commission, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse komisjoni ettepanekut ning arvestades, et: </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Article 6c of Council Regulation (EEC) No 729/70 of 21 April 1970 on the financing of the common agricultural policy (1), as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 929/79 (2), fixed the amount of financial assistance which may be charged to the European Agricultural Guidance and Guarantee Fund (EAGGF), Guidance Section, for the period 1980 to 1984; whereas this amount was fixed in proportion to requirements for improving the agricultural structures of the Community of Nine; </inglise>
<eesti> n&otilde;ukogu 21. aprilli 1970. aasta m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 729/70 (&uuml;hise p&otilde;llumajanduspoliitika rahastamise kohta, (1) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 929/79 (2)) artikliga 6c on kindlaks m&auml;&auml;ratud rahalise abi summa, mida v&otilde;ib ajavahemikul 1980-1984 katta Euroopa P&otilde;llumajanduse Arendus- ja Tagatisfondi (EAGGF) arendusrahastust; k&otilde;nealune summa on kehtestatud v&otilde;rdeliselt &uuml;heksaliikmelise &uuml;henduse p&otilde;llumajandusstruktuuride t&otilde;hustamise n&otilde;uetega; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the appropriations considered necessary for the application of Council Regulation (EEC) No 355/77 of 15 February 1977 on common measures to improve the conditions under which agricultural products are processed and marketed (3), as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 1820/80 (4), and mentioned in Article 16 (3) of the said Regulation will, from 1 January 1981, be insufficient to cover the additional cost of applying the aforesaid Regulation in Greece; </inglise>
<eesti> n&otilde;ukogu 15. veebruari 1977. aasta m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 355/77 (p&otilde;llumajandussaaduste ja -toodete t&ouml;&ouml;tlemis- ja turustamistingimuste parandamise &uuml;hismeetmete kohta, (3) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 1820/80 (4)) kohaldamiseks vajalikuks peetud assigneeringud, mida on nimetatud k&otilde;nealuse m&auml;&auml;ruse artikli 16 l&otilde;ikes 3, on alates 1. jaanuarist 1981 eespool nimetatud m&auml;&auml;ruse Kreekas kohaldamise lisakulude katmiseks ebapiisavad; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas these amounts must be adjusted, pursuant to Annex II, Chapter I, second part, point C. 1 and point E. 1 of the 1979 Act of Accession, to meet the increased requirements of agriculture in the Community, in order not to reduce the effect of the activities of the EAGGF, Guidance Section, </inglise>
<eesti> l&auml;htuvalt 1979. aasta &uuml;hinemisakti II lisa I peat&uuml;ki teise osa punkidest C.1 ja E.1 tuleb k&otilde;nealuseid summasid kohandada &uuml;henduse suurenenud p&otilde;llumajandusn&otilde;uete t&auml;itmiseks, et mitte v&auml;hendada EAGGFi arendusrahastu tegevuse m&otilde;ju, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> In Article 6c of Regulation (EEC) No 729/70, the figure "3 600" is hereby replaced by "3 755". </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 729/70 artiklis 6c asendatakse number "3600" numbriga "3755". </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> Article 16 (3) of Regulation (EEC) No 355/77 is hereby replaced by the following: </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 355/77 artikli 16 l&otilde;ige 3 asendatakse j&auml;rgmisega: </eesti>
<inglise> "3. </inglise>
<eesti> "3. </eesti>
<inglise> The estimated cost of the common measure financed by the Fund for the period from 1 January 1978 to 31 December 1982 is 646 million European units of account, i.e. 122 million European units of account per year for the period 1978 to 1980 and 140 million European units of account per year for the period 1981 to 1982". </inglise>
<eesti> Fondi poolt ajavahemikul 1. jaanuar 1978-31. detsember 1982 kaetava &uuml;hismeetme hinnangkulu on 646 miljonit Euroopa arvestus&uuml;hikut, s.t 122 miljonit Euroopa arvestus&uuml;hikut aastas ajavahemikul 1978-1980 ja 140 miljonit Euroopa arvestus&uuml;hikut aastas ajavahemikul 1981-1982." </eesti>
<inglise> Article 3 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 3 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on the third day following its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub kolmandal p&auml;eval p&auml;rast Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas avaldamist. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 22 December 1980. </inglise>
